    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>a12-11745_4ex99d1.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>EX-99.1\n<TEXT>\n\n\n<html>\n<head>\n\n  </head>\n<body lang=\"EN-US\">\n<div style=\"font-family:Times New Roman;\">\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;text-align:right;\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-weight:bold;\">Exhibit 99.1</font></b></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\"><img width=\"280\" height=\"60\" src=\"g117454mm01i001.jpg\"></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;text-align:right;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">May&nbsp;11, 2012</font></p>\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;text-align:right;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">Dear McEwen Mining Shareholders,</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">Please find below the El Gallo Complex development update and a story of how McEwen Mining is helping improve the communities surrounding its operations.</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">To date, 190,500 tonnes of material grading 1.29 gpt gold has been stockpiled representing approximately 2 months of production.</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">Key development highlights over the past two weeks are:</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> Crushing plant 60% complete</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> Process plant 60% complete</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> Heap leach expansion 50% complete</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">To view the El Gallo Development Photo Update, please click <u>here.</u></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">To view McEwen Mining&#146;s Community Story, please click <u>here.</u></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"93%\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:.25in;width:93.34%;\">\n<tr>\n<td width=\"42%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:42.34%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><b><i><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;\">For further information contact:</font></i></b></p>    </td>\n<td width=\"4%\" valign=\"bottom\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:4.14%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:1.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>    </td>\n<td width=\"53%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:53.52%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:1.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>    </td>   </tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"42%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:42.34%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>    </td>\n<td width=\"4%\" valign=\"bottom\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:4.14%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>    </td>\n<td width=\"53%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:53.52%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>    </td>   </tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"42%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:42.34%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-weight:bold;\">Jenya   Meshcheryakova</font></b></p>    </td>\n<td width=\"4%\" valign=\"bottom\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:4.14%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:1.0pt;font-weight:bold;\">&nbsp;</font></b></p>    </td>\n<td width=\"53%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:53.52%;\">\n<p style=\"